<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 10:07:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡永无休止的任期是以色列的毒瘤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-never-ending-tenure-is-israels-malignant-disease/0000018c-fa20-d517-af9d-fe3e08560000</link><description>随着以色列与哈马斯的战争即将进入第 100 天，政府必须将遣返人质作为首要任务 - 即使以停火为代价。开普敦代理——突显内塔尼亚胡政府在各方面的失败程度</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 04:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-never-ending-tenure-is-israels-malignant-disease/0000018c-fa20-d517-af9d-fe3e08560000</guid></item><item><title>深挖：哈马斯不会放弃，以色列国防军远未实现其目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/digging-in-hamas-isnt-giving-up-idf-far-from-achieving-its-goals/0000018c-f9d3-dd94-a9cc-fbff27910000</link><description>由于内塔尼亚胡的极右翼盟友对他虎视眈眈，他可能会坚持一个难以实现的目标——消灭哈马斯——从而放弃一个更容易实现的目标：人质协议</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 04:00:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/digging-in-hamas-isnt-giving-up-idf-far-from-achieving-its-goals/0000018c-f9d3-dd94-a9cc-fbff27910000</guid></item><item><title>美国、英国打击也门胡塞武装；以色列和哈马斯接近达成协议向人质运送药品</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-live/israel-to-counter-south-african-genocide-accusations-at-international-court-of-justice/0000018c-fbaa-dd94-a9cc-fbeeb7c10000</link><description>红海航运遭受数月袭击后，英国和美国在也门打击伊朗支持的胡塞武装 ■ 卡塔尔即将与哈马斯敲定协议，向加沙的以色列人质运送药品 ■ 以色列高等法院驳回因战争而驱逐内塔尼亚胡的请愿 ■ 以色列挫败伊斯兰国两名东耶路撒冷居民策划的袭击 ■ 以色列国防军发现法医证据，表明哈马斯在汗尤尼斯地下新发现的隧道中扣押了人质 ■ 布林肯表示，以色列与该地区合作，开辟通往巴勒斯坦国的道路，将孤立伊朗</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 03:31:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-live/israel-to-counter-south-african-genocide-accusations-at-international-court-of-justice/0000018c-fbaa-dd94-a9cc-fbeeb7c10000</guid></item><item><title>“在我按照与生俱来的权利去以色列旅行之前，我并不关心自己是不是犹太人。然后我的整个世界都变了”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-01-12/ty-article/.highlight/i-didnt-care-about-being-jewish-until-i-went-on-birthright-my-whole-world-changed/0000018c-fb82-dd94-a9cc-fbee842a0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名美国人在遇到一系列先知后决定成为一名拉比，而一个以色列家庭在父亲完成加沙几个月的预备役后正在休息</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 02:58:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-01-12/ty-article/.highlight/i-didnt-care-about-being-jewish-until-i-went-on-birthright-my-whole-world-changed/0000018c-fb82-dd94-a9cc-fbee842a0000</guid></item><item><title>台上台下，奥哈德·纳哈林在加沙战争中传达了强有力的信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/on-stage-and-off-ohad-naharin-conveys-a-powerful-message-amid-gaza-war/0000018c-fb01-d517-af9d-ff3fc49a0000</link><description>“人们称我为以色列的诽谤者，但诽谤以色列这个定居者救世主右翼的是我们的政府。他们认为以色列国防军的行动应该继续下去，士兵和人质的死亡是可以理解的代价。巴特谢瓦舞蹈团编舞奥哈德·纳哈林拒绝闭嘴跳舞</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 02:29:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/on-stage-and-off-ohad-naharin-conveys-a-powerful-message-amid-gaza-war/0000018c-fb01-d517-af9d-ff3fc49a0000</guid></item><item><title>美国：伊朗是胡塞武装和其他组织袭击以色列的主要推动者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/u-s-iran-is-primary-enabler-of-houthis-and-other-groups-attacking-israel/0000018c-fb6d-d517-af9d-ff7fb9bb0000</link><description>在此之前，美国领导的联军袭击也门胡塞武装目标，以回应数月来对红海海上交通的袭击</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 02:23:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/u-s-iran-is-primary-enabler-of-houthis-and-other-groups-attacking-israel/0000018c-fb6d-d517-af9d-ff7fb9bb0000</guid></item><item><title>七名以色列人回忆起他们在哈马斯被囚禁期间的磨难：“每天都有人在身体和灵魂上杀死一些东西”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/seven-israelis-recall-their-ordeal-in-hamas-captivity-every-day-kills-something-inside/0000018c-f9d9-dd94-a9cc-fbfd31340000</link><description>战争已经过去近 100 天了，而且还被关押在加沙地带。七名人质返回，但将父母、孩子、兄弟姐妹和朋友留在加沙，他们描述了他们所经历的一切，并敦促采取一切措施立即将剩余的俘虏带回家</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 00:09:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/seven-israelis-recall-their-ordeal-in-hamas-captivity-every-day-kills-something-inside/0000018c-f9d9-dd94-a9cc-fbfd31340000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方禁止针对加沙战争的抗议活动，理由是无法保护公众、防止暴力，</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-bars-protests-against-gaza-war-says-police-cant-protect-public-prevent-violence/0000018c-fa19-d1b3-a79e-fedbd1e40000</link><description>人权组织猛烈抨击阻止犹太和阿拉伯团体在海法示威的决定</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 22:22:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-bars-protests-against-gaza-war-says-police-cant-protect-public-prevent-violence/0000018c-fa19-d1b3-a79e-fedbd1e40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长可能无法避免对内塔尼亚胡是否适合任职的裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-may-not-be-able-to-avoid-ruling-on-netanyahus-fitness-for-office/0000018c-fa0a-dd94-a9cc-faee69fb0000</link><description>几个月后，如果内塔尼亚胡政府仍然完好无损，总理将不得不每天花几个小时在审判中作证，同时还要管理国家 ■ 最高法院可能已经停止了司法改革，但对裁决的仔细审查也令人担忧</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 21:08:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-may-not-be-able-to-avoid-ruling-on-netanyahus-fitness-for-office/0000018c-fa0a-dd94-a9cc-faee69fb0000</guid></item><item><title>南非是否已经破坏了以色列对国际法院种族灭绝指控的防御？</title><link>h