flights-to-israel/0000018c-f95d-dd94-a9cc-fbfd0b7c0000</link><description>飞往以色列的航班竞争加剧，导致机票价格较12月份全面大幅下跌，而飞往尚未竞争的目的地的票价则保持不变</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 17:40:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/prices-drop-as-international-airlines-resume-flights-to-israel/0000018c-f95d-dd94-a9cc-fbfd0b7c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列冰球联合会向体育仲裁法院提出上诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-ice-hockey-federation-appeals-to-court-of-arbitration-for-sport/0000018c-f949-dd94-a9cc-fbed46f70000</link><description>在 U20 男子世界锦标赛举行前 12 天，国际冰球联合会宣布禁止以色列参加比赛，“出于对所有参赛者安全的担忧” ■ 以色列称这一决定是“反犹太主义”，并向 CAS 提出上诉</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 17:37:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-ice-hockey-federation-appeals-to-court-of-arbitration-for-sport/0000018c-f949-dd94-a9cc-fbed46f70000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡支持本格维尔，表示以色列监狱长不会延长任期</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/backing-ben-gvir-netanyahu-says-israels-prison-chief-wont-have-term-extended/0000018c-f95d-d517-af9d-fd7f92de0000</link><description>尽管战时内阁同意不改变像她这样的高级职位，但凯蒂·佩里作为最高监狱长的任期预计将于一月下旬结束</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 16:43:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/backing-ben-gvir-netanyahu-says-israels-prison-chief-wont-have-term-extended/0000018c-f95d-d517-af9d-fd7f92de0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部阿拉伯城市汽车爆炸 男子丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/man-killed-in-car-explosion-in-arab-city-in-central-israel/0000018c-f94d-dd94-a9cc-fbed31050000</link><description>蒂拉发生大规模爆炸，导致一名 30 多岁男子丧生，这是本周这座阿拉伯城市发生的第二起凶杀案</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 16:26:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/man-killed-in-car-explosion-in-arab-city-in-central-israel/0000018c-f94d-dd94-a9cc-fbed31050000</guid></item><item><title>艾曼·奥德仍然相信两国解决方案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ayman-odeh-still-believes-in-the-two-state-solution/0000018c-f3f1-da04-a7df-f3f54f5a0000</link><description>艾曼·奥德 (Ayman Odeh) 16 岁时，被辛​​贝特 (Shin Bet) 安全部门叫去进行一系列关于他的政治活动的谈话。 40 多岁时，他是以色列犹太人最喜欢的阿拉伯政治家。现在他退出政党政治，但这并不是因为他放弃了更美好未来的梦想</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 16:25:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ayman-odeh-still-believes-in-the-two-state-solution/0000018c-f3f1-da04-a7df-f3f54f5a0000</guid></item><item><title>与真主党的战争是不可避免的。但以色列应该发起这一行动吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-11/ty-article-opinion/.premium/a-war-with-hezbollah-is-inevitable-but-should-israel-initiate-it/0000018c-f7d5-d432-a7ae-fffdf0e50000</link><description>以色列现在应对真主党及其挑衅有重要的战略理由。但黎巴嫩战争可能会将美国自由派选民中不断高涨的反以色列情绪转变为一场完美风暴。这将是一场以色列从未经历过的冲突</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 15:45:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-11/ty-article-opinion/.premium/a-war-with-hezbollah-is-inevitable-but-should-israel-initiate-it/0000018c-f7d5-d432-a7ae-fffdf0e50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列男子被控刺伤妻子、打伤儿子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-charged-with-stabbing-and-killing-wife-wounding-son/0000018c-f902-df8a-adbf-fb7eb4260000</link><description>起诉书指控 Asher Bohbot 对其 15 岁的儿子犯有严重谋杀罪和严重殴打罪，当时儿子在事件中试图阻止他。一位家人的熟人表示，布布特以前殴打过他的妻子，她曾考虑与他离婚</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 15:22:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-charged-with-stabbing-and-killing-wife-wounding-son/0000018c-f902-df8a-adbf-fb7eb4260000</guid></item><item><title>从被毁坏的家中撤离后，来自加沙边境的以色列孩子在特拉维夫重新开始学校</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/evacuated-from-a-devastated-home-israeli-kids-from-gaza-border-restart-school-in-tel-aviv/0000018c-f8e3-dd94-a9cc-faef01000000</link><description>大约三周前，大约 400 名雷伊姆居民从最南端城市埃拉特的酒店房间收拾行李，他们在 10 月 7 日袭击事件后从家中撤离后一直住在那里，开始了生活的新篇章。这次是在特拉维夫的赫茨尔街</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 15:11:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/evacuated-from-a-devastated-home-israeli-kids-from-gaza-border-restart-school-in-tel-aviv/0000018c-f8e3-dd94-a9cc-faef01000000</guid></item></channel></rss>